"1. For permanent hoardings on property owned by any individual or organisation other than KMC the following papers are to be submitted: a. Attested copy of Agreement between R/O & Ad. Agency; b. Declaration in the form of a davit before 1st class Magistrate in prescribed format by Ad. Agency; c. NOC in the form of a davit by R/O (Landlord) in prescribed format;
d. NOC from Advt. Dept. in favour of Ad. Agency; e. Self attested copy of updated property tax receipt from R/O (Landlord);
f. Attested copies of PAN/EPIC of Applicant(s) & R/O (Landlord)/lessee or sub-lessee/occupier; g. Self attested copy of current receipt of CE (Trade License) of Ad. Agency
h. 3 copies of sketch plan duly signed by KMC approved /empaneled structural engineer and advertising agency & endorsed by landlord; i. Wind Pressure & structural stability certificate from KMC empaneled structural engineer; j. Building stability certificate (Load Bearing Capacity) from KMC empaneled structural engineer; k. Copy of GST Registration Certificate of the applicant; l. Copy of Location Map of the proposed hoarding; m. Any other additional document. 2. For advertisement on KMC property following papers are to be submitted: a. One sketch of the advertisement with proper dimension duly sign by applicant;
b. Photograph showing location where Indicator Board/GSB will be installed; c. Self attested copy of current Trade License of applicant; d. Copy of Work Order from client, if any; e. NOC from Advertisement Department in favour of Ad Agency, if any; f. Copy of GST Registration Certificate; g. Any other additional document(s). 3. For advertisement on vehicle following papers are to be submitted: a. Work order (in case of advertisement will be done through agency) from competent authority;
b. Certificate of Enlistment/Trade License of the applicant; c. Detail list of Bus/Tram(s);  d. Details of vehicle/tableau; e. Copy of registration certificate from RTO; f. Copy of fitness certificate;
g. Copy of PUC certificate; h. Copy of Insurance Certificate; i. Copy of the logo/advertisement to be displayed (in case of advertisement on vehicle/ tableau); j. Copy of GST Registration Certificate of the applicant; k. Any other additional document"
